# pcapGo — Project Rules

## Overview
A self-hosted web app for uploading and analyzing network packet captures (.pcap/.pcapng). Wireshark-style 3-pane inspection, statistical analysis, and AI-powered per-conversation diagnostics via any OpenAI-compatible LLM.

